Eadie Adams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eadie_Adams 0 Eadie Adams (August 8, 1907 – March 30, 1983) was an American film singer and film actress. She appeared in several films between 1935 and 1937. Several of Adams' credits include Big City, The 13th Man, After the Thin Man, Sinner Take All, Reckless, I'll Love You Always and Restless Knights.
